    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hello @divya2012,\r\n\r\nWhat you should do for that to work consistently, is making a `connectRangeSlider` widget. You can read up on how to make a connector in [this guide](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/guides/customization.html) and read the specific documentation for [`connectRangeSlider`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/connectors/connectRangeSlider.html) to know which information is used exactly.\r\n\r\nDoes that help you enough? ",
